<descript>
<abstract>Global Land Cover 2000 resampled to 6/120 arcdegrees using GDAL utilities. The original map can be obtained from http://bioval.jrc.ec.europa.eu/products/glc2000/glc2000.php. The methodology is explained in detail in: "Fritz, S. et al. 2003. Harmonisation, mosaicing and production of the Global Land Cover 2000 database. JRC report EUR 20849 EN, Luxembourg, 41 p."</abstract>
<purpose>Intended use: (multipurpose) global soil mapping and monitoring, species distribution modelling, environmental modelling.</purpose>
</descript>
